		<div id="comment_body_65249695"><p>I pretty much only use my Google speaker in the kitchen for casting podcasts and kitchen timers.</p><p>Over the last year or so, the casting functionality has constricted to the point where I need to use very, very explicit commands to do podcast navigation.</p><p>Commands like "Skip ahead X minutes/seconds" or "Stop playback" or "Subtract X minutes from Timer Y" no longer work at all.</p><p>I sometimes now even get crazy stuff like "Ok, playing <i>some random song by an artist you've never heard of</i>" in response to a "set a timer.<span class="substr"> </span></p></div>
	</div>

